import React from 'react'
import Hero from '../Components/Hero'

export default function About() {
  return (
    <>
      <Hero 
        cName="hero"
        heroImg = ""
        title="We are about Education"
        text="We provide the best education to our students."
        btnClass="btn"
        buttonText = "Get Enrolled"
        url="/"
      />
    </>
  )
}
